<p><strong>当“三折叠”遇上校园</strong></p><p><br></p><p><span style="color: rgb(23, 140, 175);"><strong>三折叠，怎么折，都有面</strong></span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(23, 140, 175);"><strong>三折叠，怎么折，都迷人</strong></span></p><p>青春是一幅广阔的画卷</p><p>校园以独特的光彩</p><p>点亮了一幅广阔的画卷</p><p>校园以独特的光彩</p><p>点亮了最耀眼的一隅</p><p>今天</p><p>让我们以<span style="color: rgb(23, 140, 175);"><strong>“三折叠”</strong></span>的方式</p><p><span style="color: rgb(23, 140, 175);"><strong>邀您记录校园的独特记忆~</strong></span></p><p><br></p><p><strong>01</strong></p><p><br></p><p><strong>四时风光 美在其中 </strong></p><p><img src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/ic9uyOCtJsStUMeABUjDAskNKEePmEUPtHw28XMcVY2IlO1mtgfIH37EGoFpEkn4Go5icjFUWviaEFB0FEuWGwTMQ/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&from=appmsg&tp=wxpic&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1" alt="图片" data-href="" style="width: 100%;"/></p><p><img src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/ic9uyOCtJsStUMeABUjDAskNKEePmEUPt39ibj4RmfADmibAyZ89bDIHJvvv6ts3iaHT2JxgTdIKeKLzjAcpMrdwKg/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&from=appmsg&tp=wxpic&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1" alt="图片" data-href="" style="width: 100%;"/></p><p><img src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/ic9uyOCtJsStUMeABUjDAskNKEePmEUPtv9CYRicma1Eto0t9Mo8SAibURHIAUDRQBRwEuEsFaXvPpLIejicLtX2NA/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&from=appmsg&tp=wxpic&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1" alt="图片" data-href="" style="width: 100%;"/></p><p><img src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/ic9uyOCtJsStUMeABUjDAskNKEePmEUPtR3gMTUxxagvq30NFDtK9mr3SyAqros2ATbKBkcSxXlNgMerTYZvb2Q/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&from=appmsg&tp=wxpic&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1" alt="图片" data-href="" style="width: 100%;"/></p><p><img src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/ic9uyOCtJsStUMeABUjDAskNKEePmEUPtcDxEgQibn8S63Y4a8IVzgy8dh9ZngLeGXfiaX8eeZ70Lr82m0JMg6vQA/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&from=appmsg&tp=wxpic&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1" alt="图片" data-href="" style="width: 100%;"/></p><p><img src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/ic9uyOCtJsStUMeABUjDAskNKEePmEUPtxDoN7ibaV0ROFAqiaOtlDvIov7wDWDpFFa3uTvxsibtjyIKibEutntias3w/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&from=appmsg&tp=wxpic&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1" alt="图片" data-href="" style="width: 100%;"/></p><p><strong>三折叠，怎么折都好看</strong></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p style="text-align: center;">树影婆娑，光影斑驳</p><p style="text-align: center;">漫步在铺满落叶的校道上</p><p style="text-align: center;">感受着冬日的温馨与活力</p><p style="text-align: center;">每一幕都是校园风光的冬日限定</p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><strong>02</strong></p><p><br></p><p><strong>一日三餐 美食荟萃</strong></p><p><img src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/ic9uyOCtJsStUMeABUjDAskNKEePmEUPtBq1jpOlUibZarvlyGI1p88IUWDIortvqjsWAmTNdVAt681bxp4vENKA/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&from=appmsg&tp=wxpic&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1" alt="图片" data-href="" style="width: 100%;"/></p><p><img src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/ic9uyOCtJsStUMeABUjDAskNKEePmEUPt8pL6efdBEbEomiaZwbjlEEic5ujiagXrGkD7jI9MJuXsAAr6PtzU2D2EA/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&from=appmsg&tp=wxpic&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1" alt="图片" data-href="" style="width: 100%;"/></p><p><img src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/ic9uyOCtJsStUMeABUjDAskNKEePmEUPt7v16DIWyhJVqmV1WXTj57RicOuP1xbGe6vxFg7v7Oh1sxzlDN1O3ib0Q/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&from=appmsg&tp=wxpic&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1" alt="图片" data-href="" style="width: 100%;"/></p><p><img src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/ic9uyOCtJsStUMeABUjDAskNKEePmEUPtg1oGjhhw06ltPqISusMQdP0ANvngtZCGANw646SGl4QKDwTefBjZug/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&from=appmsg&tp=wxpic&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1" alt="图片" data-href="" style="width: 100%;"/></p><p><img src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/ic9uyOCtJsStUMeABUjDAskNKEePmEUPtw4iaIQMoibB6S3cCYeFZFlfAufv5qWgbbxKWYoI7xosLVhBicxQ8DiaicLA/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&from=appmsg&tp=wxpic&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1" alt="图片" data-href="" style="width: 100%;"/></p><p><img src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/ic9uyOCtJsStUMeABUjDAskNKEePmEUPt9comXT8VXkZah4p6A5Bme6XSnnzjD4FsyKvicVJr30vsnKdgZZ3maNA/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&from=appmsg&tp=wxpic&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1" alt="图片" data-href="" style="width: 100%;"/></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><strong>三折叠，怎么折都美味</strong></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">四季流转，一日三餐</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">冬味袭来，暖胃又暖心</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">美食荟萃，风味创新</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">每一口都是对味蕾的极致诱惑</span></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><strong>03</strong></p><p><br></p><p><strong>逐光而上 编织理想</strong></p><p><br></p><p><img src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/ic9uyOCtJsStUMeABUjDAskNKEePmEUPtztnRicYC2UE8HBMUNA9mOBOeJ6KqDU9fDwcKrfmZA9O3iaPh7ofic8sZg/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&from=appmsg&tp=wxpic&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1" alt="图片" data-href="" style="width: 100%;"/></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><img src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/ic9uyOCtJsStUMeABUjDAskNKEePmEUPtDrItkO0JsIFfRgaIVQNsLa4kIDTkL52FmDbSTQvso50QD8EwLUuVaw/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&from=appmsg&tp=wxpic&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1" alt="图片" data-href="" style="width: 100%;"/></p><p><br></p><p><img src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/ic9uyOCtJsStUMeABUjDAskNKEePmEUPtuW6RPPcjUPKFsUp6x6HPw5hsPsnSfQUJyqQtvTaClOTB2dZTcTKaRg/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&from=appmsg&tp=wxpic&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1" alt="图片" data-href="" style="width: 100%;"/></p><p><br></p><p><img src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/ic9uyOCtJsStUMeABUjDAskNKEePmEUPtLgc8Dk0GWrKRNQGLRZXuIFdpE3f6vBzg0EqvZW9268oKaGJ8KWVPew/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&from=appmsg&tp=wxpic&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1" alt="图片" data-href="" style="width: 100%;"/></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><img src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/ic9uyOCtJsStUMeABUjDAskNKEePmEUPtFzN6mqFw7uBR7OEazIDQRj2Xck2fWmrrgtrE5RrEJG1G8TncCibLw2Q/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&from=appmsg&tp=wxpic&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1" alt="图片" data-href="" style="width: 100%;"/></p><p><br></p><p><strong>三折叠，怎么折都优秀！</strong></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p style="text-align: center;">光影流转，书香四溢</p><p style="text-align: center;">此刻的时间仿佛静止</p><p style="text-align: center;">笔尖划过，键盘敲打</p><p style="text-align: center;">诠释着莘莘学子</p><p style="text-align: center;">每一个字都是对知识的热爱和追求</p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><strong>04</strong></p><p><br></p><p><strong>意气风发 活力四射</strong></p><p><img src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/ic9uyOCtJsStUMeABUjDAskNKEePmEUPtF737dqlyViar3QAiaW1E6X1MCmErwz6L0UfKibl5Fa5WEuQ9ibBMFgprzQ/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&from=appmsg&tp=wxpic&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1" alt="图片" data-href="" style="width: 100%;"/></p><p><img src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/ic9uyOCtJsStUMeABUjDAskNKEePmEUPtTs6q21u54nibPGZqhQe97etaiaLIE3ShdEAeicK0KfNPaDRbicwAf9fupw/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&from=appmsg&tp=wxpic&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1" alt="图片" data-href="" style="width: 100%;"/></p><p><img src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/ic9uyOCtJsStUMeABUjDAskNKEePmEUPtaGFHvxJDrUDQKwjHZAvmxyKKtTia3RHw5bgoKypNLm6DbiaCh30Akp4w/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&from=appmsg&tp=wxpic&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1" alt="图片" data-href="" style="width: 100%;"/></p><p><img src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/ic9uyOCtJsStUMeABUjDAskNKEePmEUPtbt9nWfDKVpWq7FpFljYs3sa72d7CN5MumWdtb6xbomy5X8kMFb3nRQ/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&from=appmsg&tp=wxpic&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1" alt="图片" data-href="" style="width: 100%;"/></p><p><img src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/ic9uyOCtJsStUMeABUjDAskNKEePmEUPtLpbJ92PC5j2gYroemyASmIbgXFSGvzjnGZdI5yCzaA1t7sMcL3ydgw/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&from=appmsg&tp=wxpic&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1" alt="图片" data-href="" style="width: 100%;"/></p><p><img src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/ic9uyOCtJsStUMeABUjDAskNKEePmEUPtkWWo15ts6qcSWZyeRjTNiaVaoTLTLh7BKLDNUGFqNMRCZxsGbHbswjA/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&from=appmsg&tp=wxpic&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1" alt="图片" data-href="" style="width: 100%;"/></p><p><br></p><p><strong>三折叠，怎么折都活力！</strong></p><p><br></p><p>奔跑，跳跃，舞动</p><p>激情四溢，挥洒汗水</p><p>斗志昂扬，奋力角逐</p><p>每一个动作都彰显着青春活力</p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><strong>“三折叠”，每一面皆是精彩</strong></p><p><br></p><p>无论哪一面都用心折叠</p><p>每一折都绚丽多彩</p><p>记录青春的成长与蜕变</p><p>邂逅那独一无二的自己</p><p><strong>生活远不止有三面</strong></p><p><span style="color: rgb(23, 140, 175);"><strong>愿各位在不同的“折面”里</strong></span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(23, 140, 175);"><strong>绽放属于自己的光彩</strong></span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(23, 140, 175);"><strong>折出有“面儿”的青春！</strong></span></p>